Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain　消した記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:48.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely　物語の常が今見せる言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
