Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}目的を忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:04.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:10.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:14.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:23.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:32.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:41.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:50.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的記憶
