Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}無論怎麼做都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:04.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}別人定義出的你 不是真實的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:10.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}堅持自我的力量 才是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:14.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}這就是我的信念
