Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:23.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:32.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會堅持到最後 不會放棄
